OL,3,CReform sacks Simon Dudley as party
OL,4,Cspokesperson over offensive Grenfell
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FReform UK has sacked its housing
OL,8,Fspokesperson Simon Dudley over
OL,9,Foffensive comments he made about the
OL,10,FGrenfell fire.
OL,12,FSpeaking at a press conference on
OL,13,FWednesday, Nigel Farage described
OL,14,FDudley's comments as "deeply
OL,15,Finappropriate", and "rather shocking",
OL,16,Fadding thar Dudley had been "dealt
OL,17,Fwith" and was no longer a party
OL,18,Fspokesperson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
