OL,3,CReform sacks Simon Dudley as party
OL,4,Cspokesperson over offensive Grenfell
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FIn an interview published on Wednesday
OL,13,Fby Inside Housing, Dudley said housing
OL,14,Fsafety regulations had "swung too far
OL,15,Fthe wrong way" on regulation after the
OL,16,Fdeadly blaze at the west London tower
OL,17,Fblock in 2017, calling Grenfell a
OL,18,F"tragedy" but adding "everyone dies in
OL,19,Fthe end".
